snippet.title: 5 News
snippet.description:
We bring you the stories that matter to you, from around the world and across the UK.

🎥 We post daily playlists with the biggest news of the day, interviews, special reports and investigations.

📺 Catch us on TV on Channel 5 every weekday 5-6pm

📱 Get in touch with us on WhatsApp at +44 7555 500 501

🎧 Listen to "How Did We Get Here? Explaining The News" wherever you get your podcasts: https://podfollow.com/how-did-we-get-here-explaining-the-news

Subscribe to the channel here to stay up to date - http://bit.ly/5NewsSub
Follow 5 News on Twitter to get in touch - https://twitter.com/5_News
Message us on Facebook to share your opinion - https://www.facebook.com/c5News
See the latest pictures and videos on Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/c5news/

Our flagship, hour-long programme at 5pm is watched on Channel 5 by up to a million viewers, with regular news updates throughout the day.
